- The Culmination Faction: 11-member Council bloc. Believe ancient civilization "culminated" (transcended) not died. Led by Drest. Academic arm: Aldric Mourne.
- Expansion Faction: 6-member Council bloc. Territorial/economic expansion. Drove Ashford Blockade ~45 years ago.

